目的多为营销和宣传。一些企业还会冠以「与公司共进退」的说法，对转发内容、发圈频次、点赞数甚至个人头像作出要求，并将员工转发情况与其收入和职业发展挂钩。 「对于职工是否在微信朋友圈转发工作信息，应当遵循自愿原则。」北京市京都律师事务所律师张雁峰指出，要求职工在个人朋友圈转发工作信息，或涉嫌侵犯隐私权和言论自由。 「朋友圈」，公司怎能想占就占"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-22e353c320e6a949cd5e6b5760b17142_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610029723"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4InY3S0rjikPRlEAMaCDk3ODQyODY5IJrJiKUGMAA4KUAPcgk2MTAwMjk3MjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1688368123.805065", "card_id": "Q_609808731", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待「七成应届生毕业后还需父母经济支持」一事？毕业后你需要父母经济支持了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2023 年毕业季，微博、新浪新闻面向应届毕业生发起的「毕业生问卷调查」显示，四成应届生毕业后选择直接就业。北上广深一线城市吸引力下降，仅排名第三，就业重心持续下沉。71.4% 的应届生毕业后还需要父母的经济支持。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e470aba858a9e4ce9439779820ae6399_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609808731"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4InY3S0rjikPRlEAMaCDk3NzkzNzIxIIOBgKUGMAA4YkAQcgk2MDk4MDg3MzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1688368123.805413", "card_id": "Q_425747510", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么有的人学习效果这么好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有的人坚持学习花很多的时间学习效果都不理想，而有的人花很少的时间学习效果却很好，这是智商问题？还是个人学习方法的问题？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-411803c313f56abe7e474afc